bilingual.source: Gandhi gave India and the world the principles of nonviolence and honesty.
bilingual.target: 甘地为印度和世界带来了非暴力和诚实的原则。

bilingual.source: We all know that honesty is an important value and that lying is wrong, but who can honestly say that they've never told a lie?
bilingual.target: 我们都知道诚实是一个重要的价值观，说谎是错误的，但谁能诚实地说他们从未撒过谎呢？
诚实是一种重要的美德。

bilingual.source: He is in doubt about her honesty.

bilingual.target: 他的诚实是不容置疑的。

list.abstract: 《Honesty》是美国歌手Billy Joel (比利·乔尔)演唱的歌曲。收录在Billy Joel1978年10月1日发行的专辑《52nd Street》中。
Honesty，周华健所属专辑Blue Bird中歌曲。作词、作曲、编曲、演唱均为周华健本人。 语种英语。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh. I love Honesty Island. And that's the truth.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哦，我可喜欢诚实岛了，这是真的。

yingyinNormal.en: Thank you for telling us. Honesty is always the best policy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢谢你的坦诚，诚实总是上上策。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, go ahead. Tell her what you think. Grandma loves honesty. It's okay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 来吧，告诉她你是怎样想的，外婆喜欢诚实的，没关系的。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah. Well, you can still tell Queller the truth. I think she'll respect your honesty.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你还是可以跟库娜说真相啊，我想她会尊重你的诚实的。

yingyinNormal.en: Candor value honesty and order. They tell the truth, even when you wish they wouldn't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 诚实派注重诚信和秩序，无论你是否愿意，他们始终只陈述事实。

yingyinNormal.en: As you open yourself up to possibility, the most important thing I can tell you today, is to open yourself up to honesty, to telling the truth to each other, to being honest with yourselves, and to being honest about the world we live in.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你需要对各种可能性持开放态度，今天我要讲的最重要的一点就是，对诚实保持开放态度，相互之间说老实话，对自己诚实，也对我们所生活的世界保持诚实。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《Facebook COO谢丽尔·桑德伯格哈佛演讲》

yingyinNormal.en: Is that nice? No, but it's honest, and it sounds like you could use a little more honesty in you relationship.
yingyinNormal.zh: 需要那么毒吗？不用，但至少诚实啊，而且感觉起来你们的感情也需要多一点真诚。

yingyinNormal.en: Smackle, remember how you asked us to let you know when your refreshing honesty crosses over into... Get to it, Bubbles! Now!
yingyinNormal.zh: 史麦科，还记得你让我们在你过于诚实的时候提醒你吗？有话直说，泡泡！现在就是！

yingyinNormal.en: Because power in the hands of those who lack honesty, lacks a moral compass. And without a moral compass, power runs amok.
yingyinNormal.zh: 权力如果掌握在不诚实的人手里，便会失去道德的指引。而失去了道德的指引，权力便会胡作非为。

yingyinNormal.en: We lost Goofball Island. That means she can lose Friendship and Hockey and Honesty and Family. You can fixed this, right, Joy?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们失去了淘气岛，这意味着她也可能失去友谊，冰球，诚实，还有家庭岛，你可以搞定这一切的，对不对，"乐乐"？

yingyinNormal.en: What does she know about honesty? Serena.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她还知道什么叫坦诚相待？瑟琳娜。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't doubt the honesty of young Pegg. That is not at all what I asked.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不怀疑佩格先生的正直。这是答非所问。

yingyinNormal.en: Del. We thank Wendell for his honesty. But, again: that makes this case simpler.
yingyinNormal.zh: 戴尔，我们感谢温德尔的坦诚，但依然，这让案子简单多了。

yingyinNormal.en: Look, Ross look, I'm on board about this totally honesty thing, I am. Just not about stuff that's gonna get you in trouble.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我也赞成要坦承，真的，不过会惹麻烦的事还是少说为妙。

yingyinNormal.en: But I wish you would decide that honesty is the best policy. In the meanwhile, try to take a break from.. while you're in London.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我希望你能对他如实相告。与此同时，趁着去伦敦这段时间尽量放松一下吧。

yingyinNormal.en: I know you all understand better that most that real progress requires authentic, an authentic way of being honesty and, above all, empathy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道你们对此再清楚不过，真正的进步需要真实的方式，真诚对待，将心比心。

yingyinNormal.en: You can make the world fair for everyone, expect honesty from yourself and each other, demand and create truly equal opportunity, not eventually, but now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们能够让世界对于每个人更加公平。对自己和他人，你们需要坦诚相待。要求并创造真正平等的机会，不是最终，而是现在。

yingyinNormal.en: So this is your opinion of me? Thank you for explaining so fully. Perhaps these offences might have been overlooked had not your pride been hurt by my honesty in admitting scruples about our relationship.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这就是你对我的看法？谢谢，只怪我老老实实地把我以前 一误再误、迟疑不决的原因说了出来，所以伤害了你的自尊心，否则你也许就不会计较我得罪你的这些地方了。
